text: tavada pratiksepa kalavun (nira) ginna veta idiripat karanu labana dinaye “meya satyaya nove da” (yæyi vimasanu labati). “apage paramadhipati mata divura (eya) eseya” yæyi ovuhu pavasati. “ese nam numbala pratiksepa karamin siti dæ hetuven ema danduvama numbala bhukti vindinu” yæyi ohu pavasayi
